  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine whether local injection of bevacizumab might halt
      and or cause regression of pterygium growth. This may enable earlier treatment and prevention
      of pterygium growth into the patient's line of sight thereby limiting the need for surgery
      and improving quality of life for patients with pterygia.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
